WEBVTT

00:00.500 --> 00:04.500
Welcome to RestoreAssist. In this tutorial, I'll show you how to sign in to your account.

00:05.700 --> 00:14.700
Open your browser and go to restoreassist dot a u. The site loads in under two seconds.

00:15.700 --> 00:24.700
Enter your email and password, then tap the Sign In button.

00:25.700 --> 00:35.000
You're now signed in. Your dashboard shows active jobs, upcoming inspections, and your workspace health score.
